wiki.summary: "Saturn" is a song by American singer-songwriter SZA and the lead single of Lana, the upcoming reissue of her second studio album, SOS. It was surprise-released through Top Dawg Entertainment and RCA Records on February 22, 2024. Read more on Last.fm.
